{"tid":798018,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】搶佔車道起糾紛　寶馬紋身司機持刀襲撃電單車男反被殺","createTime":"2018-08-29T03:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T06:08:03.000Z","uid":202698,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fdf2a6a7f98d9e774e193d8ac75e96ef7ec95345","tid":798018,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T03:44:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VrTlNcrz60M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVrTlNcrz60M&d=vRx0i4A9Lt2JCJ9PTFs9w6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=5601c122\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VrTlNcrz60M</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/114200_4b2db0ffcd42184cabe7350ba62658fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F114200_4b2db0ffcd42184cabe7350ba62658fa.jpg&h=6e4466c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/114202_1abddf5f78d346b47039afc03aa608ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F114202_1abddf5f78d346b47039afc03aa608ee.jpg&h=a4dd3c5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/114207_257f9f67467247dadf3a311a57a8d61b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F114207_257f9f67467247dadf3a311a57a8d61b.jpg&h=b6a3500c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/228657/%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%87%E5%AF%B6%E9%A6%AC%E8%BB%8A%E6%92%9E%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%BB%8A-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%8C%81%E5%88%80%E8%A5%B2%E6%92%83%E5%8F%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%96%AC-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E9%A8%8E%E5%A3%AB%E6%AD%A3%E7%95%B6%E9%98%B2%E8%A1%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BA%258B%2F228657%2F%25E6%25B1%259F%25E8%2598%2587%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%2592%259E%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%2588%2580%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2592%2583%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2596%25AC-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E9%25A8%258E%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%2595%25B6%25E9%2598%25B2%25E8%25A1%259B&d=vRx0i4A9Lt2JCJ9PTFs9w6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=2de16f25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/228657/%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%87%E5%AF%B6%E9%A6%AC%E8%BB%8A%E6%92%9E%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%BB%8A-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%8C%81%E5%88%80%E8%A5%B2%E6%92%83%E5%8F%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%96%AC-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E9%A8%8E%E5%A3%AB%E6%AD%A3%E7%95%B6%E9%98%B2%E8%A1%9B</a><br />\n<br />\n馬路的事，拔刀相「助」？江蘇崑山市一名駕駛寶馬的司機前晚（27日）在馬路上與一名電動車騎士發生行車糾紛，<span style=\"color: red;\">寶馬司機其後居然從車廂拿出長刀襲擊騎士，不過這位司機「刀法」不佳，揮刀時長刀掉落地上，隨即被騎士拾起反撃，最終導致寶馬司機搶救不治。</span>但不少網民都認為對騎士的行為屬正當防衛。<br />\n<br />\n寶馬突駛入非機車道肇禍<br />\n<br />\n據事發片段可見，涉事路段的交通燈正亮起紅燈，當時36歲的寶馬司機劉某突然把座駕右駛轉入非機車道，並疑似與非機車道上的一輛電動車發生碰撞，寶馬一名男乘客當時曾下車與41歲的電動車騎士于某爭執，不過于某其後已把電動車牽上行人路。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但寶馬司機劉某後來又下車推撞及踢打于某，並於車廂拿出長刀，對空揮刀企圖襲撃于某。其間劉某不慎倒地，于某即奪過掉落地上的長刀追斬劉某，身中多刀的劉某最終經搶救不治</span>，而于某亦於事件中受傷，目前沒生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n律師：騎士行動已超防衛範疇<br />\n<br />\n有國內律師根據事發片段認為，<span style=\"color: red;\">于某的行為已涉嫌故意傷害致人死亡</span>。因于某持刀反擊後，劉某當時已經逃竄，但于某仍然持刀追斬，雖然從片段所看，劉某被斬的部位都並不致命，但明顯已身中多刀，這已經超出了防衛的範疇。<br />\n<br />\n律師又指，國內故意傷害致人死亡的刑期一般是10年以上至死刑，不過，本案中，于某並非蓄意作案，兇器也非他所持有，相信這些因素會在法院開庭量刑時予以考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民熱議：<br />\n<br />\n「開寶馬車還藏刀，這是隨時準備戰鬥啊！」<br />\n「騎車的人太冤枉，正常走的非機動車道，無故被蹭了、還被打了、最後被斬了，正當防衛，對方死了，結果還要他來承受。」<br />\n「那種情況下，電動自行車主在恐懼和憤怒的支配下已沒辦法作出正常的判斷。」<br />\n「機動車闖非機動車道，居然說成行車問題引發口角。」"},{"pid":"1bcdc885ad89b60675e09175460b361e6e302e51","tid":798018,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T03:52:10.000Z","msg":"咁都要正當防衛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 執起追住嚟斬都叫正當防衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47fea5b62bff0a6fb72e59de130f47c52512a263","tid":798018,"uid":162316,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T03:55:02.000Z","msg":"貼埋條屍出黎唔加慎入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb3111e24abaab53378058f17a6575ea1c7dbf4","tid":798018,"uid":202698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"47fea5b62bff0a6fb72e59de130f47c52512a263","tid":798018,"uid":162316,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T03:55:02.000Z","msg":"貼埋條屍出黎唔加慎入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:24:44.000Z","msg":"唔小心img左，唔好意思"},{"pid":"5ca581cca2db7e23ddf025ff0f2cd9243d7d553d","tid":798018,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:35:07.000Z","msg":"屌你呢d反而有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee9b856331afb8bca42fccc88939222fc4914c3","tid":798018,"uid":3122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1bcdc885ad89b60675e09175460b361e6e302e51","tid":798018,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T03:52:10.000Z","msg":"咁都要正當防衛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 執起追住嚟斬都叫正當防衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:36:46.000Z","msg":"好似你咁唔識反擊咩<br />\n垃圾"},{"pid":"e5058703ae67cb021ca2661552729f056996ac37","tid":798018,"uid":23468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ee9b856331afb8bca42fccc88939222fc4914c3","tid":798018,"uid":3122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1bcdc885ad89b60675e09175460b361e6e302e51","tid":798018,"uid":23468,"like":0,"di